{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For motorcycle enthusiasts looking to spend enjoyable time at their computer, Motorcycle Night Ride offers a wonderful option with its soothing atmosphere.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For those who want to escape the hectic pace, focus on scenic views, and simply enjoy the ride, this game delivers exactly that kind of experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A dynamic atmosphere enriched with sunsets, nighttime rides, and various weather conditions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- No race stress, no chasing after objectives\u2014just scenery, the sound of the motorbike, and a relaxing vibe.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Simple and smooth driving mechanics instead of complex controls.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The freedom to ride without the stress of traffic or the pressure of competition.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game focuses on peace and relaxation rather than speed and adrenaline.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s perfect for unwinding after a long day and enjoying a pleasant experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/aciklama_1.png?t=1740074894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy night driving with different engines. Each engine offers a unique experience with its unique sound and driving feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/motors.gif?t=1740074894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/aciklama_3.png?t=1740074894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Drive on more than 10 maps enriched with majestic city lights, quiet countryside, coastal roads and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/harita.gif?t=1740074894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/aciklama_2.png?t=1740074894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Enjoy the roads endlessly, without the stress of missions or racing. Just the scenery, the sound of the engine and a peaceful driving experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/yol.gif?t=1740074894\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/aciklama_4.png?t=1740074894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a detailed and realistic crash system, react differently every time you crash. Recover your bike and continue your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/extras/kaza.gif?t=1740074894\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Those tired of competitive games,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Players seeking a tranquil gaming experience,  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Anyone who wants to feel the wind through the sound of a motorbike\u2014this game is truly calming.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Put on your helmet, gently twist the throttle, and savor the freedom\u2014even if it\u2019s just on screen!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3358360?t=1740074894","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740074894","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358360/897bcad8